headline: Hagerty, Inc. (HGTY) Misses Q3 Earnings Estimates
summary: Hagerty (HGTY) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -37.50% and 1.67%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
